  "architecture_rule": "Every dataset and both tasks execute all shared representation modules; only learned parameters and gates differ. Supervised Packet-module weights are trained independently from each task's own split and are never transferred across tasks. Flow adds packet_to_flow_proj and aggregation after the shared packet representation.",
  "shared_core_modules": [
    "per_flow_split_guard",
    "field_aware_header_policy",
    "current_packet_structural_encoder",
    "current_packet_byte_payload_encoder",
